### Create a new order
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "eventOrders": [
    {
      "eventId": 1,
      "ticketCount": 2
    },
    {
      "eventId": 2,
      "ticketCount": 1
    }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID
GET {{host}}/api/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get orders for current user
GET {{host}}/api/orders/user
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get all orders (admin only)
GET {{host}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update order status
PATCH {{host}}/api/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "status": "CANCELLED"
}

### Cancel an order
POST {{host}}/api/orders/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Refund an order
POST {{host}}/api/orders/1/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get orders by status (PENDING, COMPLETED, CANCELLED, REFUNDED)
GET {{host}}/api/orders/status/PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get orders by event ID
GET {{host}}/api/orders/event/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get orders within a date range
GET {{host}}/api/orders/daterange?start=2023-01-01&end=2023-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
